Employers


Post Positions on Handshake






Post Positions on Handshake
Thank you for your interest in UIC engineering and computer science talent! UIC utilizes Handshake to enable employers to post, manage, and view applications for job, internship, and co-op positions all in one easy-to-use platform at no cost. 
Please note that if you reach out to the Engineering Career Center with an opportunity for students we will direct you to post the position(s) to Handshake first. This enables you to select from the widest applicant pool possible, in addition to creating a more equal opportunity search process for you and our students. 
Once you have posted your position(s) to Handshake, we encourage you to reach out to us directly so we can help to answer questions about how to use Handshake, as well as increase interest and applications to your positions!




Not sure how to start?
Check out Handshake's guide for Employers!




All set?
Log in to Handshake








